on in non-reversing mirror environments\nand could impact the implementation of general screen-based AR systems in other\ndomains.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2016 15:45:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2016 15:02:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-08"}
